@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_iuguim(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = wp.cos(wp.sin(wp.abs(v0 + 0.78)))
    tmp = (wp.exp((v0 + 0.42 / tmp + 0.44)) - (v1 - (v0 + 0.61 / tmp + 0.78)))
    v0 = (v2 - wp.exp(0.19))
    v1 = (0.28 / wp.exp(v0))
    v0 = ((v1 / 0.16) / 0.62)
    v0 = 0.42
    data[tid] = v0
